- Kami dah mati. Ya, samalah.
- Ya.

73
00:07:12,682 --> 00:07:14,391
Penjana perisai kau itu...

74
00:07:14,392 --> 00:07:16,768
Bukan penjana perisai. Ya, kami tahu.

75
00:07:16,769 --> 00:07:20,021
Rasanya itu maklumat yang patut dikongsi.

76
00:07:20,022 --> 00:07:21,731
Ya, kami dah cuba.

77
00:07:21,732 --> 00:07:22,899
Antena patah.

78
00:07:22,900 --> 00:07:24,151
- Salah dia.
- Salah dia.

79
