Voyager Beta.

99
00:11:09,168 --> 00:11:10,086
Ada isyarat?

100
00:11:11,420 --> 00:11:14,090
Negatif, Voyager Alpha. Voyager Gamma?

101
00:11:14,674 --> 00:11:17,008
Kosong belaka di sini.

102
00:11:17,009 --> 00:11:19,636
Eksperimen belon awak tak berkesan, Manja.

103
00:11:19,637 --> 00:11:22,555
Jom pasang antena pada van dan pandu saja.

104
00:11:22,556 --> 00:11:24,974
{\an8}Voyager Gamma, rupa bumi tak sekata

105
00:11:24,975 --> 00:11:26,726
{\an8}dan banyak hutan di Hawkins,

106
00:11:26,727 --> 00:11:30,563
jadi kenderaan tak wajar digunakan
untuk kesan tag telemetri.

107
00:11:30,564 --> 00:11:34,275
{\an8}"Wajar"? Dah enam jam
kita buat eksperimen belon awak.

108
00:11:34,276 --> 00:11:37,028
{\an8}<i>Ya, tapi sebaik saja
kita menigasegi isyarat,</i>

109
