"Lepaskan..."

114
00:11:59,218 --> 00:12:01,095
Orang berani pasti bertuah.

115
00:12:04,432 --> 00:12:06,308
{\an8}Saya dah dapat lokasi Dustin.

116
00:12:06,892 --> 00:12:08,268
Lepas belon, Voyager.

117
00:12:08,269 --> 00:12:10,019
- Boleh ulang?
- Kejap. Apa?

118
00:12:10,020 --> 00:12:14,066
Ia perlu naik lebih tinggi.
Lepaskan belon.

119
00:12:18,195 --> 00:12:19,572
Negatif 80!

120
00:12:20,197 --> 00:12:21,865
Negatif 44.

121
00:12:21,866 --> 00:12:25,160
Saya tarik balik, Manja.
Awak memang genius!

122
00:12:25,161 --> 00:12:28,164
Terima kasih.
Biar saya kira. Tunggu sekejap.

123
00:12:41,969 --> 00:12:46,264
<i>Kau akan jadi pengintip aku</i>

124
00:12:46,265 --> 00:12:50,019
<i>buat kali terakhir.</i>

125
00:12:55,483 --> 00:12:56,317
Will.

126
00:12:58,194 --> 00:13:00,153
Hopper baru hubungi mak di radio.

127
00:13:00,154 --> 00:13:02,406
Max selamat. Dia dah keluar.

128
00:13:04,325 --> 00:13:07,077
Hei, ini berita baik.

129
00:13:07,995 --> 00:13:10,830
Ini semua takkan berlaku
kalau bukan sebab kamu.

130
00:13:10,831 --> 00:13:12,124
Semuanya pasti okey.

131
00:13:12,792 --> 00:13:15,001
Tapi sampai bila, mak?

132
00:13:15,002 --> 00:13:17,879
Kalau betul cakap Lucas, hari ini harinya,

133
