Dia tahu. Dia dah tahu sejak awal lagi.

137
00:13:31,811 --> 00:13:35,439
Dalam ramai-ramai orang di Hawkins,
ada sebab dia pilih saya.

138
00:13:36,482 --> 00:13:40,109
Sebab dia tahu saya lemah,

139
00:13:40,110 --> 00:13:43,071
dan dia tahu dia boleh kawal saya.

140
00:13:43,072 --> 00:13:44,697
Tak betul.

141
00:13:44,698 --> 00:13:46,950
Betul, mak. Betul.

142
00:13:46,951 --> 00:13:48,744
Saya wadah dia.

143
00:13:49,745 --> 00:13:52,664
Wadah untuk menyalurkan kuasa dia,

144
00:13:52,665 --> 00:13:53,749
<i>mengintip</i>

145
00:13:54,333 --> 00:13:56,585
<i>dan membina.</i>

146
00:13:57,878 --> 00:14:00,213
"Membina"?

147
00:14:00,214 --> 00:14:01,924
Terowong-terowong itu.

148
00:14:02,883 --> 00:14:05,010
Ia tak terbentuk sendiri dari pintu.

149
00:14:05,594 --> 00:14:10,932
<i>Setiap malam, saya terhubung dengan sarang
dan mengawal akar-akar menjalar</i>

150
00:14:10,933 --> 00:14:12,851
<i>untuk membentuk terowong</i>

151
00:14:12,852 --> 00:14:16,188
<i>dan menjangkiti dunia kita
dengan Tempat Terbalik.</i>

152
00:14:16,981 --> 00:14:19,358
Begitu ramai orang mati disebabkan saya.

153
00:14:20,484 --> 00:14:22,695
<i>Kalau saya mampu buat semua itu,</i>

154
00:14:23,529 --> 00:14:27,032
apa agaknya dia mampu buat
dengan 12 lagi budak macam saya?

155
00:14:27,616 --> 00:14:29,158
Dengar sini.

156
00:14:29,159 --> 00:14:32,161
Segala benda yang terjadi
bukannya salah kamu.

157
00:14:32,162 --> 00:14:33,080
Faham tak?

158
00:14:33,664 --> 00:14:35,999
Pasal rancangan besar dia pula,

159
00:14:36,000 --> 00:14:38,960
dia takkan ada 12 wadah
atau apa-apalah namanya.

160
00:14:38,961 --> 00:14:42,338
Dia baru kehilangan Holly.
Holly tahu budak lain di mana.

161
00:14:42,339 --> 00:14:46,468
Sayang, ini belum berakhir.
Perjuangan kita masih panjang.

162
00:14:47,636 --> 00:14:48,679
Mak silap.

163
00:14:49,471 --> 00:14:50,890
Mak silap.

164
00:14:51,432 --> 00:14:52,974
Ini salah saya.

165
00:14:52,975 --> 00:14:53,934
Tidak.

166
00:14:54,602 --> 00:14:55,853
Tidak, sayang.

167
00:15:04,737 --> 00:15:06,280
Gerak!

168
00:15:17,750 --> 00:15:20,168
<i>Saya tak nampak di mana Holly akan sedar.</i>

169
00:15:20,169 --> 00:15:22,880
Tapi saya agak,

170
00:15:23,923 --> 00:15:26,008
di mana-mana pun Vecna tahan dia,

171
00:15:26,842 --> 00:15:28,802
mesti di Tempat Terbalik.

172
00:15:30,220 --> 00:15:31,221
Jadi,

173
00:15:32,222 --> 00:15:35,600
saya suruh dia balik ke rumah.

174
00:15:35,601 --> 00:15:37,644
Rumah? Maksudnya rumah kami?

175
00:15:37,645 --> 00:15:40,313
Kita kena masuk semula ke Tempat Terbalik.

176
00:15:40,314 --> 00:15:42,815
- Rekahan terdekat di mana?
- Cornwallis.

177
00:15:42,816 --> 00:15:44,525
Lebih kurang 2.5 kilometer.

178
00:15:44,526 --> 00:15:45,985
<i>Lucas, dengar tak?</i>

179
00:15:45,986 --> 00:15:46,945
- Robin.
- Ya.

180
00:15:46,946 --> 00:15:47,863
<i>Lucas!</i>

181
00:15:50,282 --> 00:15:52,158
Aku tak boleh cakap sekarang.

182
00:15:52,159 --> 00:15:56,079
Vecna dah bunuh askar-askar itu,
jadi mudah nak masuk ke MAC.

183
00:15:56,080 --> 00:15:57,914
Tak. Mesti ada pasukan lain.

184
00:15:57,915 --> 00:15:59,540
Saya boleh pecahkan plat.

185
00:15:59,541 --> 00:16:04,212
Maksud kamu, Holly terperangkap
di bawah plat keluli?

186
00:16:04,213 --> 00:16:06,422
Bunyinya mungkin merisaukan,

187
00:16:06,423 --> 00:16:10,259
tapi dia bukannya dihempap
oleh kepingan keluli besar. Dia...

188
00:16:10,260 --> 00:16:11,511
Bagaimana nak kata?

189
00:16:11,512 --> 00:16:15,056
- Ada dunia di bawah dunia kita...
- Di bawah plat itu.

190
00:16:15,057 --> 00:16:16,224
Tempat Terbalik.

191
00:16:16,225 --> 00:16:18,893
Ia macam Hawkins, tapi jauh lagi suram.

192
00:16:18,894 --> 00:16:20,561
Semua orang.

193
00:16:20,562 --> 00:16:22,355
Okey, mesti kamu tak percaya,

194
00:16:22,356 --> 00:16:26,026
tapi Erica dan En. Clarke
dah jumpa Dustin dan yang lain.

195
00:16:27,194 --> 00:16:30,781
Baiklah. Lagi senang
kalau mereka yang cari Holly.

196
00:16:33,409 --> 00:16:35,953
Baik kita cepat. Mereka datang.

197
00:16:47,923 --> 00:16:50,551
Hei, hei. Mak okey tak?

198
00:16:51,135 --> 00:16:52,427
Mak okey, Michael.

199
00:16:52,428 --> 00:16:54,303
Tak. Maaflah, puan tak okey.

200
00:16:54,304 --> 00:16:58,100
Puan boleh kena jangkitan,
perdarahan dan berhenti bernafas.

201
00:16:58,600 --> 00:17:02,854
Kalau kamu fikir saya rela baring saja
sedangkan anak saya perlukan saya,

202
00:17:02,855 --> 00:17:06,024
kamu memang dah hilang akal. Mari pergi.

203
00:17:06,025 --> 00:17:08,651
Mak, mak. Betul cakap dia.

204
00:17:08,652 --> 00:17:10,279
Tak apa. Pergilah.

205
00:17:10,863 --> 00:17:12,989
Hei, mak dah selamatkan kami.

206
00:17:12,990 --> 00:17:14,532
Mak selamatkan kami.

207
00:17:14,533 --> 00:17:17,118
Ajaibnya, mak masih hidup, okey?

208
00:17:17,119 --> 00:17:20,413
Tapi percayalah cakap saya
yang kami mampu uruskannya.

209
00:17:20,414 --> 00:17:23,541
Mungkin banyak lagi makhluk itu di luar.

210
00:17:23,542 --> 00:17:25,334
Namanya Demogorgon. Saya tahu.

211
00:17:25,335 --> 00:17:29,797
Banyak benda saya perlu cerita
tentang Tempat Terbalik dan El,

212
00:17:29,798 --> 00:17:31,632
tapi mak cuma perlu tahu,

213
00:17:31,633 --> 00:17:34,886
kumpulan ini selamatkan Will
waktu tiada siapa mampu.

214
00:17:34,887 --> 00:17:36,179
Kami berjaya.

215
00:17:36,180 --> 00:17:38,389
Kami akan selamatkan Holly pula.

216
00:17:38,390 --> 00:17:42,436
Kami akan bawa dia balik.
Saya janji. Okey?

217
00:17:44,021 --> 00:17:44,855
Ya?

218
00:17:56,200 --> 00:17:58,493
En. Clarke, terima kasih sebab tolong.

219
00:17:58,494 --> 00:17:59,660
Belum lagi.

220
00:17:59,661 --> 00:18:02,288
Kami menigasegi kedudukan Dustin ke sini,

221
00:18:02,289 --> 00:18:03,748
di tempat saya berdiri.

222
00:18:03,749 --> 00:18:06,042
Tapi waktu kami sampai, dia hilang.

223
00:18:06,043 --> 00:18:08,462
Dia bukan di sini. Dia di bawah sana.

224
00:18:09,463 --> 00:18:10,756
Apa?

225
00:18:11,507 --> 00:18:12,758
Kau tak beritahu dia?

226
00:18:13,300 --> 00:18:14,759
- Aku...
- Beritahu apa?

227
00:18:14,760 --> 00:18:16,512
Biar betul!

228
00:18:17,554 --> 00:18:18,847
Biar betul.

229
00:18:19,598 --> 00:18:21,308
Hei, sini! Sini!

230
00:18:23,143 --> 00:18:24,602
Saya jumpa dia!

231
00:18:24,603 --> 00:18:26,480
Saya jumpa Dustin!

232
00:18:32,236 --> 00:18:33,946
- Saya tak dengar.
- Sabar.

233
00:18:35,322 --> 00:18:37,824
<i>Ada sesiapa tak? Saya ulang, ini Dustin.</i>

234
00:18:37,825 --> 00:18:39,200
Dustin, ini Mike.

235
00:18:39,201 --> 00:18:42,370
Holly lari daripada Vecna,
dan dia akan ke rumah aku.

236
00:18:42,371 --> 00:18:45,998
Pergi ke sana secepat mungkin
dan jumpa Holly. Dengar tak?

237
00:18:45,999 --> 00:18:49,460
<i>Holly bukan di rumah.
Kami jumpa Holly. Aku ulang, kami...</i>

238
00:18:49,461 --> 00:18:50,963
Dustin, tak jelas.

239
00:18:51,672 --> 00:18:52,673
Dustin?

240
00:18:54,716 --> 00:18:58,428
Saya dah hilang akal,
atau memang dia cakap dia dah jumpa Holly?

241
00:19:00,347 --> 00:19:03,141
Baiklah, rapat dengan dinding.

242
00:19:03,142 --> 00:19:04,559
Kenapa dia di makmal?

243
00:19:04,560 --> 00:19:07,145
Mesti makmal itu sehala dengan rumah aku.

244
00:19:07,146 --> 00:19:09,730
Dia tiba-tiba jumpa Dustin? Logikkah?

245
00:19:09,731 --> 00:19:10,648
Tak logik pun,

246
00:19:10,649 --> 00:19:12,775
tapi kita memang perlukan tuah.

247
00:19:12,776 --> 00:19:13,693
Amen.

248
00:19:13,694 --> 00:19:17,321
Maaf. Saya masih tak faham.
Dustin di bawah plat itu?

249
00:19:17,322 --> 00:19:18,657
- Ya.
- Tak dihempap.

250
00:19:19,241 --> 00:19:20,409
Tunggu sekejap.

251
00:19:33,046 --> 00:19:35,465
Ya, ada kamera di sepanjang rekahan itu.

252
00:19:36,383 --> 00:19:38,759
Saya ada penganalisis spektrum di kelab.

253
00:19:38,760 --> 00:19:41,929
Kalau kesan isyarat RF,
saya boleh sekat pemancaran.

254
00:19:41,930 --> 00:19:42,931
Menarik.

255
00:19:43,932 --> 00:19:45,559
Tapi cara awak rumit sangat.

256
00:19:46,393 --> 00:19:49,103
Alford tak boleh dapat lebih banyak mata?

257
00:19:49,104 --> 00:19:50,855
Empat daripada enam cubaan.

258
00:19:50,856 --> 00:19:54,025
Reggie akan jadi pemain ulung, percayalah.

259
00:19:54,026 --> 00:19:55,360
Walsh tak boleh...

260
00:19:59,531 --> 00:20:01,116
Itu baru sikit.

261
00:20:38,070 --> 00:20:39,946
Awak nak ikut tak, Manja?

262
00:20:39,947 --> 00:20:41,490
Kita nak masuk?

263
00:20:42,658 --> 00:20:44,201
Kita akan masuk.

264
00:20:46,203 --> 00:20:47,828
Steve!

265
00:20:47,829 --> 00:20:49,205
Dustin!

266
00:20:49,206 --> 00:20:50,539
Steve!

267
00:20:50,540 --> 00:20:52,124
Nancy! Holly!

268
00:20:52,125 --> 00:20:53,585
Jonathan!

269
00:20:59,883 --> 00:21:01,592
Selamatkah bernafas di sini?

270
00:21:01,593 --> 00:21:02,844
Tak pasti.

271
00:21:03,762 --> 00:21:04,721
Okey.

272
00:21:05,430 --> 00:21:07,807
Mike, macam mana di bawah sana?

273
00:21:07,808 --> 00:21:10,185
Mike? Mike!

274
00:21:11,228 --> 00:21:12,437
Aku dah jumpa dia.

275
00:21:13,605 --> 00:21:14,690
Syukurlah.

276
00:21:25,450 --> 00:21:26,410
Nancy?

277
00:21:28,120 --> 00:21:29,037
Mana dia?

278
00:21:29,579 --> 00:21:30,872
Mana Holly?

279
00:21:36,503 --> 00:21:38,297
- Apa itu?
- Apa?

280
00:21:39,631 --> 00:21:40,507
Holly.

281
00:21:50,976 --> 00:21:53,769
Nancy!

282
00:21:53,770 --> 00:21:55,563
- Holly!
- Nancy, tolong aku!

283
00:21:55,564 --> 00:21:58,190
- Nancy, tolong! Turunkan aku!
- Holly!

284
00:21:58,191 --> 00:21:59,942
Nancy! Nancy, tolonglah!

285
00:21:59,943 --> 00:22:00,901
Holly!

286
00:22:00,902 --> 00:22:02,654
Nancy!

287
00:22:08,869 --> 00:22:13,373
<i>Macam ada benda tangkap dia,
tapi kami tak nampak apa-apa.</i>

288
00:22:16,084 --> 00:22:17,252
Mesti dia.

289
00:22:19,296 --> 00:22:21,173
Vecna. Mesti dia.

290
00:22:23,050 --> 00:22:23,883
<i>Mike?</i>

291
00:22:23,884 --> 00:22:26,927
Holly okey tak, Mike? Mike, dengar tak?

292
00:22:26,928 --> 00:22:29,473
Aku ulang, Holly okey tak?

293
00:23:16,895 --> 00:23:18,897
Jangan risau, Holly.

294
00:23:19,856 --> 00:23:22,692
Semuanya akan berakhir tak lama lagi.

295
00:23:24,611 --> 00:23:28,532
Semuanya akan berakhir.

296
00:23:33,412 --> 00:23:36,540
<i>Ia sejenis syaitan,
syaitan dari dunia itu.</i>

297
00:23:37,207 --> 00:23:38,959
Dia boleh kawal raksasa,

298
00:23:40,293 --> 00:23:41,585
alihkan Humvee

299
00:23:41,586 --> 00:23:43,130
dan tepis api.

300
00:23:45,757 --> 00:23:47,175
Peluru tak berkesan.

301
00:23:47,759 --> 00:23:49,260
Semuanya tak berkesan.

302
00:23:49,261 --> 00:23:50,887
Itu bukan pertempuran...

303
00:23:52,889 --> 00:23:54,641
tapi pembunuhan.

304
00:23:59,771 --> 00:24:03,274
Mula-mula anjing mutan di hospital.
Sekarang syaitan di MAC?

305
00:24:03,275 --> 00:24:05,568
Apa lagi akan keluar dari lubang itu?

306
00:24:05,569 --> 00:24:07,069
Atau nak tunggu kejutan?

307
00:24:07,070 --> 00:24:09,947
Kalau puan perasan,
orang kita dah berkurang.

308
00:24:09,948 --> 00:24:11,699
Pasukan bantuan akan sampai.

309
00:24:11,700 --> 00:24:14,869
Kalau ada permintaan lain,
beritahu komander unit.

310
00:24:14,870 --> 00:24:17,580
Apa nak minta
kalau tak tahu saya lawan apa?

311
00:24:17,581 --> 00:24:21,625
Kamu tak lawan apa-apa.
Ini bukan perang. Ini pencarian.

312
00:24:21,626 --> 00:24:23,419
Ada benda halang, bunuh saja.

313
00:24:23,420 --> 00:24:26,547
Kalau tak ada, fokus cari budak itu.

314
00:24:26,548 --> 00:24:29,133
Ya, cari budak itu. Tak habis-habis.

315
00:24:29,134 --> 00:24:32,179
Puan ada butang tarik
macam mainan bercakap, ya?

316
00:24:33,763 --> 00:24:36,474
Semua ini berlaku disebabkan budak itu.

317
00:24:36,475 --> 00:24:40,769
Kalau kamu buat kerja dan jumpa dia,
saya tak perlu cakap banyak kali.

318
00:24:40,770 --> 00:24:45,941
Raksasa itu akan ada di Moscow,
bunuh orang Soviet, bukan orang Amerika.

319
00:24:45,942 --> 00:24:48,277
Setiap nyawa yang dah terkorban,

320
00:24:48,278 --> 00:24:50,906
darah mereka di tangan kamu, bukan saya.

321
00:24:51,490 --> 00:24:55,911
Melainkan kamu nak senasib dengan mereka,
baik kamu jaga sikit mulut kamu!

322
00:25:00,916 --> 00:25:03,585
<i>Leftenan Akers, ini Bravo One. Dengar tak?</i>

323
00:25:06,129 --> 00:25:07,254
Ya, apa dia?

324
00:25:07,255 --> 00:25:09,424
<i>Ada pencerobohan rekahan di makmal lama.</i>

325
00:25:10,217 --> 00:25:11,301
Saya datang.

326
00:25:19,226 --> 00:25:20,101
Awak okey?

327
00:25:20,936 --> 00:25:21,811
Max.

328
00:25:27,526 --> 00:25:32,988
Jadi, baru satu saat saya tak ada,
awak dah jadi ahli sihir sekarang?

329
00:25:32,989 --> 00:25:34,740
Lebih daripada satu saat.

330
00:25:34,741 --> 00:25:37,077
Apa pun, saya bukan ahli sihir.

331
00:25:37,661 --> 00:25:39,120
Nampak macam ahli sihir.

332
00:25:40,622 --> 00:25:42,916
Hei, awak nak tengok kawasan tak?

333
00:25:45,961 --> 00:25:48,170
Jimmy "Tangan Lincah" lari
sebelum kuarantin,

334
00:25:48,171 --> 00:25:50,089
jadi kami pindah ke sini.

335
00:25:50,090 --> 00:25:52,675
Ruang bawah tanah
di belakang rak buku itu.

336
00:25:52,676 --> 00:25:54,593
Bukan Batcave, tapi lawa juga.

337
00:25:54,594 --> 00:25:57,137
Stesen dijadikan samaran. Robin DJ kami.

338
00:25:57,138 --> 00:25:59,848
- Rockin' Robin.
- Rockin' Robin. Maaf.

339
00:25:59,849 --> 00:26:01,392
Steve juruaudio dia.

340
00:26:01,393 --> 00:26:02,394
Cuba tengok.

341
00:26:15,699 --> 00:26:16,575
Hei.

342
00:26:17,450 --> 00:26:18,951
Kita akan dapatkan Holly.

343
00:26:18,952 --> 00:26:21,454
Dia seorang diri di sana, Lucas.

344
00:26:22,038 --> 00:26:25,040
Seorang diri dengan raksasa itu.

345
00:26:25,041 --> 00:26:27,960
Saya betul-betul yakin
dia boleh lari keluar.

346
00:26:27,961 --> 00:26:29,504
Saya memang bodoh.

347
00:26:30,088 --> 00:26:32,007
Awak perlu cuba.

348
00:26:32,591 --> 00:26:34,217
Saya patut tinggal di sana.

349
00:26:36,678 --> 00:26:38,305
Pastikan dia selamat.

350
00:26:39,347 --> 00:26:40,932
Lagi susah kami nanti.

351
00:26:41,474 --> 00:26:44,435
Lama awak dalam minda Vecna.
Tolong kami lawan dia.

352
00:26:44,436 --> 00:26:46,855
Tak. Saya tak mampu.

353
00:26:50,525 --> 00:26:52,901
Saya tak tahu di mana Vecna tahan Holly.

354
00:26:52,902 --> 00:26:54,487
Mujurlah saya tahu.

355
00:26:55,989 --> 00:26:58,491
Saya tahu di mana, cuma susah nak ke sana.

356
00:26:59,701 --> 00:27:01,453
Saya nak tunjuk sesuatu.

357
00:27:02,996 --> 00:27:03,912
Okey.

358
00:27:03,913 --> 00:27:09,043
Jadi, ini Hawkins,
dan ini pula Tempat Terbalik.

359
00:27:09,044 --> 00:27:12,212
Kita anggap ia dimensi lain
yang dibuka oleh Brenner,

360
00:27:12,213 --> 00:27:15,592
tapi ia sebenarnya jambatan.

361
00:27:16,176 --> 00:27:18,302
Lebih tepat, jambatan antara dimensi

362
00:27:18,303 --> 00:27:19,928
<i>yang menembusi ruang-masa.</i>

363
00:27:19,929 --> 00:27:23,682
Ia sangat tak stabil,
tapi ia disatukan oleh jirim eksotik

364
00:27:23,683 --> 00:27:27,061
yang kami jumpa
betul-betul di atas makmal itu.

365
00:27:27,062 --> 00:27:28,437
<i>Dalam fizik teori,</i>

366
00:27:28,438 --> 00:27:30,856
- jambatan ini namanya...
- Lubang ulir.

367
00:27:30,857 --> 00:27:33,942
Lubang ulir itu
menghubungkan Hawkins ke sini,

368
00:27:33,943 --> 00:27:37,529
satu lagi dunia
yang saya namakan sebagai Jurang.

369
00:27:37,530 --> 00:27:40,407
- Ada sebab?
- Alam huru-hara dan kejahatan.

370
00:27:40,408 --> 00:27:42,284
- Apa?
- D&D.

371
00:27:42,285 --> 00:27:43,869
- Ya Tuhan.
- Wah.

372
00:27:43,870 --> 00:27:46,413
Saya percaya Jurang inilah tempat asal

373
00:27:46,414 --> 00:27:49,500
Demogorgon, akar menjalar, Penguasa Minda,

374
00:27:49,501 --> 00:27:51,960
semua benda yang ada di Tempat Terbalik.

375
00:27:51,961 --> 00:27:54,046
Dulu awak usir Henry ke sana.

376
00:27:54,047 --> 00:27:57,091
<i>Lama dia hilang.
Dia muncul balik sebab Brenner.</i>

377
00:27:57,092 --> 00:27:59,009
Dia suruh saya cari Henry.

378
00:27:59,010 --> 00:28:02,554
Waktu awak terhubung dengan Jurang,
jambatan itu terbentuk.

379
00:28:02,555 --> 00:28:07,434
Henry dan bala tentera raksasa dia guna
untuk merentas masuk ke Hawkins.

380
00:28:07,435 --> 00:28:09,770
Kita kalahkan Vecna tahun lepas,

381
00:28:09,771 --> 00:28:13,065
tapi dia merentas jambatan
ke Jurang untuk pulihkan diri.

382
00:28:13,066 --> 00:28:14,024
Pengecut.

383
00:28:14,025 --> 00:28:17,653
Maknanya, selama ini,
Vecna menyorok di langit?

384
00:28:17,654 --> 00:28:19,905
Sebab itu penyusupan tak ada hasil.

385
00:28:19,906 --> 00:28:22,950
- Saya tak jumpa dia dari tab.
- Holly jatuh dari langit.

386
00:28:22,951 --> 00:28:24,952
Kenapa dia bawa budak ke sana?

387
00:28:24,953 --> 00:28:26,537
Sama macam sayalah.

388
00:28:26,538 --> 00:28:30,582
Minda budak lebih lemah, bukan?
Lebih senang dibentuk dan dikawal.

389
00:28:30,583 --> 00:28:34,253
Dia menyalurkan fikiran dan kuasa
untuk menguatkan kebolehan.

390
00:28:34,254 --> 00:28:35,879
Dia akan guna budak-budak itu.

391
00:28:35,880 --> 00:28:37,632
Menguatkan kebolehan?

392
00:28:38,174 --> 00:28:39,174
Untuk buat apa?

393
00:28:39,175 --> 00:28:40,343
Mengalihkan dunia.

394
00:28:42,512 --> 00:28:45,723
Holly kata Henry beritahu budak-budak itu

395
00:28:45,724 --> 00:28:49,561
yang mereka akan tolong dia
tarik dunia lain ke dunia kita.

396
00:28:50,687 --> 00:28:52,896
Saya tak faham waktu itu, tapi...

397
00:28:52,897 --> 00:28:55,899
Dia nak alihkan Jurang dan rempuh Hawkins.

398
00:28:55,900 --> 00:28:56,943
Bukan rempuh.

399
00:28:57,527 --> 00:28:58,569
Gabung.

400
00:28:58,570 --> 00:29:00,904
Henry bukannya pulihkan diri di Jurang.

401
00:29:00,905 --> 00:29:02,322
Dia sibuk buat rekahan

402
00:29:02,323 --> 00:29:05,492
untuk melemahkan Jurang
macam dia melemahkan Hawkins.

403
00:29:05,493 --> 00:29:07,202
Jurang dan Hawkins bertembung...

404
00:29:07,203 --> 00:29:08,203
Ia bergabung.

405
00:29:08,204 --> 00:29:09,663
Dia cipta semula dunia.

406
00:29:09,664 --> 00:29:12,833
Berapa lama diperlukan
untuk mengalihkan dunia?

407
00:29:12,834 --> 00:29:15,669
Serta-merta begini
atau ia akan mengambil masa?

408
00:29:15,670 --> 00:29:17,129
Harap-harap ada masa.

409
00:29:17,130 --> 00:29:18,297
Sebab kalau betul,

410
00:29:18,298 --> 00:29:21,091
kita perlu terbang 2,000 kaki,
masuk ke Jurang,

411
00:29:21,092 --> 00:29:24,261
bebaskan budak-budak dan bunuh Vecna
sebelum dunia bergabung.

412
00:29:24,262 --> 00:29:25,889
Kalau teori aku betul,

413
00:29:26,598 --> 00:29:28,098
dia akan mula malam ini.

414
00:29:28,099 --> 00:29:30,017
Saya benci teori awak.

415
00:29:30,018 --> 00:29:31,143
- Sama.
- Sama.

416
00:29:31,144 --> 00:29:33,812
Saya benci semua ini.

417
00:29:33,813 --> 00:29:37,317
Tapi sekurang-kurangnya,
kita dah tahu apa yang menanti

418
00:29:37,942 --> 00:29:39,194
dan apa perlu dibuat.

419
00:29:40,570 --> 00:29:41,863
Kita kena rancang.

420
00:30:03,718 --> 00:30:04,803
Maaf.

421
00:30:05,470 --> 00:30:07,638
Saya bukan nak menyibuk, tapi,

422
00:30:07,639 --> 00:30:09,307
semua orang risau.

423
00:30:10,391 --> 00:30:11,851
Dia okey tak?

424
00:30:18,024 --> 00:30:19,483
Awak dah cakap, bukan?

425
00:30:19,484 --> 00:30:22,361
Max itu cuma raksasa yang menyamar.

426
00:30:22,362 --> 00:30:25,072
Raksasa itu memperdayakan dan menipu dia.

427
00:30:25,073 --> 00:30:26,157
Mestilah.

428
00:30:26,991 --> 00:30:29,536
Macam-macam saya cuba,
tapi dia tetap degil.

429
00:30:31,079 --> 00:30:33,705
Kita perlukan dia malam ini
kalau tak nak gagal.

430
00:30:33,706 --> 00:30:36,375
Max cakap apa kepada dia?

431
00:30:36,376 --> 00:30:39,462
Benda-benda yang jahat.

432
00:30:40,255 --> 00:30:42,089
Max cakap saya culik kamu.

433
00:30:42,090 --> 00:30:43,841
- Apa?
- Awak selamatkan kami.

434
00:30:43,842 --> 00:30:44,884
Saya tahu.

435
00:30:46,344 --> 00:30:48,012
Bukan itu yang paling teruk.

436
00:30:49,097 --> 00:30:52,975
Max cakap saya bukan nak selamatkan dunia.
Saya nak hancurkannya.

437
00:30:52,976 --> 00:30:56,311
- Kenapa dia percaya?
- Sebab dia bodoh nak mampus.

438
00:30:56,312 --> 00:30:58,273
Tak, dia tak bodoh, Thomas.

439
00:30:59,274 --> 00:31:02,943
Raksasa itu sangat berkuasa,
dan dia bekerja untuk Black Thing.

440
00:31:02,944 --> 00:31:07,698
Dia meracuni minda dan menyeret Holly
daripada cahaya kepada kegelapan.

441
00:31:07,699 --> 00:31:11,159
Mungkin kita patut mengalah
dan balik saja sekarang.

442
00:31:11,160 --> 00:31:13,245
- Balik?
- Jumpa mak ayah kita.

443
00:31:13,246 --> 00:31:14,454
Matilah kita nanti.

444
00:31:14,455 --> 00:31:15,622
Apa masalah kau?

445
00:31:15,623 --> 00:31:16,957
Diamlah, bangang.

446
00:31:16,958 --> 00:31:19,167
Tolong jangan bergaduh.

447
00:31:19,168 --> 00:31:21,003
Saya tahu semua susah hati.

448
00:31:21,004 --> 00:31:22,672
Tapi mungkin Derek betul.

449
00:31:23,756 --> 00:31:27,468
Mungkin saya gagal,
dan Black Thing dah menang.

450
00:31:28,344 --> 00:31:29,971
Kita tak boleh biar saja.

451
00:31:30,555 --> 00:31:32,223
Okey? Tak boleh.

452
00:31:33,516 --> 00:31:35,309
Kami lebih kenal Holly.

453
00:31:35,310 --> 00:31:37,728
Saya kawan baik dia sejak tadika lagi.

454
00:31:37,729 --> 00:31:39,146
Debbie kawan baik kedua.

455
00:31:39,147 --> 00:31:41,440
- Dia tergila-gilakan Josh.
- Taklah.

456
00:31:41,441 --> 00:31:42,691
- Ya.
- Betul.

457
00:31:42,692 --> 00:31:46,571
Maksud saya, kami boleh sedarkan dia
kalau kami cakap dengan dia.

458
00:31:47,447 --> 00:31:49,949
Kami boleh bawa dia kembali kepada cahaya.

459
00:31:50,617 --> 00:31:52,910
Betul cakap Mary. Kami boleh buat.

460
00:31:52,911 --> 00:32:12,096
Kembali kepada cahaya.

461
00:32:14,807 --> 00:32:17,894
Kalau tengok kamera keselamatan
dan plat parit itu...

462
00:32:18,603 --> 00:32:19,812
Bukan pemotong bolt.

463
00:32:20,313 --> 00:32:22,023
Boleh dikatakan begitu, tuan.

464
00:32:28,696 --> 00:32:30,114
Dia makin cuai.

465
00:32:31,199 --> 00:32:32,241
Cincai.

466
00:32:33,076 --> 00:32:34,451
Mungkin raksasa itu.

467
00:32:34,452 --> 00:32:36,621
Raksasa pecahkan mangga dan kamera?

468
00:32:37,246 --> 00:32:38,456
